        </a></li>
    

            <li><a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/health/print/2014/08/the-secret-ebola-treatment/375525/" class="social-icon print" data-omni-click="inherit" target="_blank"><span>Print</span></a></li>
    

            <li><a href="#disqus_thread" class="social-icon comments"><span>Comments</span></a></li>
        
